  {
    "id": "US-002",
    "title": "Landing Page Hero Section",
    "description": "As a visitor, I want a hero section for our SaaS product landing page with a catchy headline, a subtitle describing the value proposition, a call-to-action button, and a background gradient or illustration. It should feel modern, bold, and inspiring.",
    "priority": "Medium",
    "status": "To Do",
    "assignee": "Thomas Martin",
    "uiProposal": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"fr\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>Landing Page – Hero</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #0b0b0b;\n      --text: #ffffff;\n      --muted: #b3b3b3;\n      --primary: #f97316; /* orange */\n      --card: #151515;\n      --border: #2a2a2a;\n    }\n\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, sans-serif;\n      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a1a, var(--bg));\n      color: var(--text);\n      min-height: 100vh;\n    }\n\n    .hero {\n      width: 100%;\n      padding: 56px 24px 40px;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: auto;\n    }\n\n    .hero-main {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 32px;\n      margin-bottom: 48px;\n    }\n\n    @media (min-width: 768px) {\n      .hero-main {\n        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;\n        gap: 48px;\n      }\n    }\n\n    .hero-content h1 {\n      font-size: 38px;\n      line-height: 1.2;\n      margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n      color: var(--primary);\n    }\n\n    .hero-content p {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: 28px;\n      max-width: 520px;\n    }\n\n    .actions {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 16px;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n    }\n\n    .btn-primary {\n      background: var(--primary);\n      color: #000;\n      border: none;\n      padding: 14px 22px;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: transform .15s ease, filter .2s ease;\n    }\n\n    .btn-primary:hover {\n      filter: brightness(1.05);\n      transform: translateY(-1px);\n    }\n\n    .btn-secondary {\n      background: transparent;\n      color: var(--text);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      padding: 14px 22px;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      cursor: pointer;\n    }\n\n    .btn-secondary:hover {\n      border-color: var(--primary);\n      color: var(--primary);\n    }\n\n    .hero-visual {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249,115,22,0.25), rgba(249,115,22,0.05));\n      border-radius: 22px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      padding: 28px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      min-height: 280px;\n    }\n\n    .mockup {\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 360px;\n      background: var(--card);\n      border-radius: 16px;\n      padding: 20px;\n      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);\n      font-size: 13px;\n    }\n\n    .mockup .line {\n      height: 10px;\n      background: #262626;\n      border-radius: 6px;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .mockup .line.short { width: 60%; }\n    .mockup .line.medium { width: 80%; }\n\n    .hero-boxes {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 20px;\n    }\n\n    @media (min-width: 768px) {\n      .hero-boxes {\n        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n      }\n    }\n\n    .hero-box {\n      background: var(--card);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 18px;\n      padding: 22px;\n      transition: transform .15s ease, border-color .2s ease;\n    }\n\n    .hero-box:hover {\n      transform: translateY(-4px);\n      border-color: var(--primary);\n    }\n\n    .hero-box h3 {\n      margin: 0 0 8px 0;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      color: var(--primary);\n    }\n\n    .hero-box p {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <section class=\"hero\">\n    <div class=\"hero-main\">\n      <div class=\"hero-content\">\n        <h1>Boostez votre productivité</h1>\n        <p>Une plateforme moderne et sécurisée pour gérer vos opérations, suivre vos performances et simplifier le quotidien de vos équipes.</p>\n        <div class=\"actions\">\n          <button class=\"btn-primary\">Démarrer maintenant</button>\n          <button class=\"btn-secondary\">En savoir plus</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hero-visual\">\n        <div class=\"mockup\">\n          <div class=\"line medium\"></div>\n          <div class=\"line\"></div>\n          <div class=\"line short\"></div>\n          <div class=\"line\"></div>\n          <div class=\"line medium\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"hero-boxes\">\n      <div class=\"hero-box\">\n        <h3>⚡ Rapidité</h3>\n        <p>Des workflows optimisés pour gagner du temps et réduire les tâches manuelles.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hero-box\">\n        <h3>🔒 Sécurité</h3>\n        <p>Vos données sont protégées avec des standards de sécurité entreprise.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"hero-box\">\n        <h3>📊 Pilotage</h3>\n        <p>Suivez vos indicateurs clés et prenez de meilleures décisions.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n</body>\n</html>"
  },
